definitions.definition: A muscle in the back of the thigh ; the most medial of the three hamstring muscles (meaning it is more to the inner of the thighs , not between the two others in one leg , which is the semitendinosus ).

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A muscle in the back of the thigh ; the most medial of the three hamstring muscles (meaning it is more to the inner of the thighs , not between the two others in one leg , which is the semitendinosus ).
